players.name: Yassine Bounou
players.summary: Yassine Bounou, also known as Bono, is a professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Saudi Pro League club Al Hilal. Born in Canada, he plays for the Morocco national team.

players.name: Munir Mohamedi
players.summary: Munir El Kajoui, known as Munir, is a professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Botola Pro club RS Berkane, whom he captains, and the Morocco national team.

players.name: El Mehdi Al Harrar
players.summary: El Mehdi Al Harrar is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper with Botola side Raja CA and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Achraf Hakimi
players.summary: Achraf Hakimi Mouh is a professional footballer who plays as a right-back for club Paris Saint-Germain. Born in Spain, he captains the Morocco national team. He is widely regarded as one of the best right-backs in the world.

players.name: Noussair Mazraoui
players.summary: Noussair Mazraoui is a professional footballer who plays as a defender for Premier League club Manchester United and the Morocco national team. As a versatile player, primarily a right-back, Mazraoui has featured at both full back positions and at centre-back.

players.name: Nayef Aguerd
players.summary: Nayef Aguerd is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a centre-back for Ligue 1 club Marseille and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Romain Saïss
players.summary: Romain Ghanem Paul Saïss is a professional footballer who plays as a centre-back or defensive midfielder for Qatar Stars League club Al Sadd. Born in France, he represents the Morocco national team.

players.name: Mohamed Chibi
players.summary: Mohamed Chibi is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a right-back for Pyramids FC, and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Jawad El Yamiq
players.summary: Jawad El Yamiq is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a centre-back for Saudi club Al-Najma and the Morocco national team. He began his professional career playing for Olympique Khouribga.

players.name: Adam Masina
players.summary: Adam Masina is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a defender or left-back for Italian Serie A club Torino and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Anass Salah-Eddine
players.summary: Anass Salah-Eddine is a professional footballer who plays as a left-back or left wing-back for Eredivisie club PSV, on loan from Serie A club Roma. Born in the Netherlands, he plays for the Morocco national team.

players.name: Abdelhamid Aït Boudlal
players.summary: Abdelhamid Aït Boudlal is a Moroccan footballer who plays as a central defender for French Ligue 1 club Rennes and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Youssef Belammari
players.summary: Youssef Belammari is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a left-back for Botola club Raja CA and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Sofyan Amrabat
players.summary: Sofyan Amrabat is a professional footballer who plays as a defensive midfielder for La Liga club Real Betis, on loan from Süper Lig side Fenerbahçe, and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Azzedine Ounahi
players.summary: Azzedine Ounahi is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for La Liga club Girona and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Ismael Saibari
players.summary: Ismael Saibari is a professional footballer who plays as a midfielder or a winger for Eredivisie club PSV Eindhoven. Born in Spain, he plays for the Morocco national team.

players.name: Eliesse Ben Seghir
players.summary: Eliesse Ben Seghir is a professional footballer who plays as a left winger or left midfielder for Bundesliga club Bayer Leverkusen. Born in France, he plays for the Morocco national team.

players.name: Oussama Targhalline
players.summary: Oussama Targhalline is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Eredivisie club Feyenoord and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Bilal El Khannouss
players.summary: Bilal El Khannouss is a professional footballer who plays as an attacking midfielder for Bundesliga club VfB Stuttgart, on loan from EFL Championship club Leicester City. Born in Belgium, he plays for the Morocco national team.

players.name: Neil El Aynaoui
players.summary: Neil Yoni El Aynaoui is a professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Italian Serie A club Roma. Born in France, he plays for the Morocco national team.

players.name: Hamza Igamane
players.summary: Hamza Igamane is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a forward for Ligue 1 club Lille and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Soufiane Rahimi
players.summary: Soufiane Rahimi is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a forward for UAE Pro League club Al Ain and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Brahim Díaz
players.summary: Brahim Abdelkader Díaz, known mononymously as Brahim, is a professional footballer who plays as an attacking midfielder or winger for La Liga club Real Madrid. Born in Spain, he plays for the Morocco national team.

players.name: Ilias Akhomach
players.summary: Ilias Akhomach is a professional footballer who plays a right winger for La Liga club Villarreal. Born in Spain, he plays for the Morocco national team.

players.name: Abde Ezzalzouli
players.summary: Abdessamad "Abde" Ezzalzouli, sometimes known as Ez Abde, is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a winger for La Liga club Real Betis and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Youssef En-Nesyri
players.summary: Youssef En-Nesyri is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a striker for Süper Lig club Fenerbahçe and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Ayoub El Kaabi
players.summary: Ayoub El Kaabi is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a striker for Super League Greece club Olympiacos and the Morocco national team.

players.name: Chemsdine Talbi
players.summary: Chemsdine Talbi is a professional footballer who plays as a winger for Premier League club Sunderland. Born in Belgium, he plays for the Morocco national team.
